0915\u0930\u0923\u201d link OR directly click the below given link. Farmer Registration Link: https://dbtagriculture.bihar.gov.in/NewRegistration.aspxSTEP 3: If you have Aadhar card, then select \u201c\u0939\u093e\u0901\u201d on screen and then click on \u201cYes\u201d button, you will be shown a page as given in the below image. If you don\u2019t have Aadhar card, you can go to nearest Aadhar registration center and apply for Aadhar card.Bihar Farmer RegistrationSTEP 4: Select any one of the two options as per your choice \u201cDEMOGRAPHY + OTP\u201d or \u201cDEMOGRAPHY + BIO-AUTH\u201d.STEP 5: Enter your Aadhar Number and the Name as per Aadhar card and the click on Authenticate, if you have selected \u201cDemography + OTP\u201d, you will receive an OTP on your Aadhar registered mobile number, verify the OTP and complete the next process.After the farmer registration, you will receive a farmer registration number of 13 digits which you can use to apply for Pradhanmantri Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana in Bihar.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}